  <brief_title>Testing Hypersensitivity to Metals in Sarcoidosis Patients by Applying the MELISA Test.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Testing Hypersensitivity to Metals in Sarcoidosis Patients With Occupational Exposure, Using the MELISA Test.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
